# Module

## Structure: Base (Abstract)

**Id**: `resource`

**Name**: Resource

**Kind**: Structure

**Description:** Base structure for all resources.

**Primitive**: Record

**Shape:**

- `id` – Identifier (resource name)
- `name` – NaturalName (resource name)
- `kind`: Natural Name (resource kind)
- `purpose` – A short description of what the resource enables.
- `description` – A short description of what the resource defines.
- `status` – One of `active`, `wip`, `broken`, `deprecated`.
- `examples` – A list of example values for the resource.

**Status:** wip

**Examples:**

- This file (self-referential)
- `.agents/domains/_artificials/structures/command__structure.md`
- `.agents/domains/tasks/structures/task__structure.md`
